        Searches for schools with the conditions given
        Parameters:
        schoolName - name of the school
        state - the state where the school is located
        location - what type of area is the school located at
        control - the type of school (e.g. private)
        numOfStuStart - number of students attending school starting amount
        numOfStuEnd - number of students attending school ending amount
        perFemStart - percentage of females attending starting amount
        perFemEnd - percentage of females attending ending amount
        satVerbalStart - average SAT Verbal score starting amount
        satVerbalEnd - average SAT Verbal score ending amount
        satMathStart - average SAT Math score starting amount
        satMathEnd - average SAT Math score ending amount
        priceStart - total expenses for a year at school starting amount
        priceEnd - total expenses for a year at school ending amount
        finAidStart - the percentage of students receiving financial aid starting amount
        finAidEnd - the percentage of students receiving financial aid ending amount
        numOfAppStart - the number of applications the school receives starting amount
        numOfAppEnd - the number of applications the school receives ending amount
        perAdmitStart - the percentage of admitted students condition starting amount
        perAdmitEnd - the percentage of admitted students ending amount
        perEnrollStart - the percentage of students enrolled starting amount
        perEnrollEnd - the percentage of students enrolled after applying ending amount
        controlStart - the control of school amount
        controlEnd - the control of school ending amount
        academicScaleStart - the scale of academic life on campus starting amount
        academicScaleEnd - the scale of academic life on campus ending amount
        socialScaleStart - the scale of social life on campus starting amount
        socialScaleEnd - the scale of social life on campus ending amount
        lifeScaleStart - the scale of life on campus starting amount
        lifeScaleEnd - the scale of life on campus ending amount
        popMajor - a list of popular majors at university
        Returns:
        list of university which matches criteria entered by user
